    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的任务：发现隐藏之物……在一切太迟之前</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Spectator 2》，在这里，你的敏锐目光和钢铁般的神经是秩序与混乱之间的唯一防线。你的任务？监视来自最阴森恐怖地点的实时安全摄像头画面，发现异常，报告它们，并希望自己足够迅速，以防现实崩塌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/f6cd658256c824c9689da18b4daa4392.poster.avif?t=1763913217\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/f6cd658256c824c9689da18b4daa4392.webm?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/f6cd658256c824c9689da18b4daa4392.mp4?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首次支持多人合作！邀请朋友一起加入分屏合作模式——两个视角是否比一个更可靠……还是更危险？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让你彻夜难眠的功能</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>监视疯狂</strong> <br>实时监控多个恐怖场景的安全摄像头。闪烁的灯光、移动的物体、本不该出现的影子——发现并报告异常，别等到太迟。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带上朋友（给自己壮胆）</strong> <br>分屏合作模式！因为一起尖叫比一个人害怕要更有趣。你们可以协作，也可以各自慌乱——无论如何，“它”正在观察着你。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逐步升级的恐怖体验</strong> <br>最开始只是微不足道的变化，但随着时间推移，异常现象会变得越来越诡异。保持专注，采取反制措施，不要让现实滑向崩溃。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/9b8f3014b12cc83cff12f15135933685.poster.avif?t=1763913217\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/9b8f3014b12cc83cff12f15135933685.webm?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/9b8f3014b12cc83cff12f15135933685.mp4?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更多致命异常</strong> <br>本次异常现象比以往更加多样、诡异且令人不安。从细微的变化到恐怖的闯入者，你的感知力将面临终极考验。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/09f588fb79246f1ccc23962396680ff5.poster.avif?t=1763913217\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/09f588fb79246f1ccc23962396680ff5.webm?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/09f588fb79246f1ccc23962396680ff5.mp4?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一局都是全新体验</strong> <br>威胁？随机生成。你的生存？无法保证。随机生成的异常现象确保每一局游戏都截然不同。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索令人毛骨悚然的美丽环境</strong> <br>从废弃的餐馆到阴森的旅馆，每个场景都经过精心设计，确保你时刻保持警惕。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/c9b91cd701c26b5b1da7abb6e4094f69.poster.avif?t=1763913217\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/c9b91cd701c26b5b1da7abb6e4094f69.webm?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/c9b91cd701c26b5b1da7abb6e4094f69.mp4?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逐步揭开的故事</strong> <br>每个地点都隐藏着秘密。新的关卡将揭示《Spectator》宇宙中的隐藏联系。每一个细节都至关重要。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存并非理所当然</strong> <br>如果你错过太多异常现象，现实将会崩溃。控制好局势……否则你将面对比“游戏结束”更可怕的后果。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/12446e5a0e5c8303d39e93f7d1836727.poster.avif?t=1763913217\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/12446e5a0e5c8303d39e93f7d1836727.webm?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358620/extras/12446e5a0e5c8303d39e93f7d1836727.mp4?t=1763913217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>那么……你真的能看得清吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你唯一的武器是你的观察力。你的唯一盟友？也许是屏幕上那些可能正在操纵你思维的恐怖景象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只是一个旁观者……还是他们也在注视着你？</p>",
